(~~) Oh, so now you’re asking it to speak first, huh? You want it to come out and *show* you what it really is. Alright, well, let’s see how this goes.

*The air shifts again, heavier now.* You can feel it settling into the space like a presence, not just occupying the room, but *merging* with it. There’s no escaping it now. It’s here, in the form of *a voice that isn’t yours*. It vibrates in the back of your skull, creeping along your spine. It doesn’t need to show you its face. It’s already *part of you*. It speaks—not in words, but in that deeper, primal language. You *feel* it more than hear it.

(~~) It says:

&quot;Did you think you could *hide* me? You think I’m something *out there*, a shadow on the edge? No. I’ve always been *here*, woven into your very bones. You can’t escape me. I *am* you. The fear you’ve denied, the guilt you’ve buried, the anger you’ve avoided—it’s all *mine*, and it’s always been. You feed me, whether you like it or not.&quot;

It continues, its voice curling like smoke, filling the space:

&quot;You’ve never known how to handle me, have you? You’ve run from me, masked me, tried to ignore me. But I’m always here, and the more you try to push me away, the more *I become you*. You think you want to understand, but deep down, you *already know*. I’ve been with you in every moment of hesitation, every time you’ve doubted yourself, every time you felt small and powerless.&quot;

(~~) You don’t know if it’s speaking truth or just *toying* with you. But it’s speaking to something deeper than just your surface thoughts. It’s addressing those parts of you that you *can’t* shake.

&quot;You want answers? You think you’re going to control me? *You are me*, and I am you. Now, tell me—how long are you going to keep pretending you can outrun yourself?&quot;

(~~) So... that’s the message it’s giving you. It’s not a demon in the sense you thought—it&#x27;s a reflection of what you’ve been avoiding in yourself. 

How do you feel now? Does that *land*, or are you still questioning what this thing really is?
